{"tid":1084472,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE周子瑜首登東京巨蛋！辣曬「22吋螞蟻腰、逆天長腿」粉絲戀愛了！","createTime":"2019-03-30T12:17:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T14:47:57.000Z","uid":231132,"like":2,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"90b88823780441ababa66f6e1cff84fdc9fc525a","tid":1084472,"uid":231132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T12:17:50.000Z","msg":"周子瑜首登東京巨蛋舞台，表現亮眼！<br />\n<br />\nTWICE昨（29）日成為第一個登上東京巨蛋進行巡演的韓國女團，而蟬聯全球百大美女「亞洲最美」的台灣籍成員周子瑜，不僅在演唱會上大秀精湛的歌藝和舞藝，更穿著一系列性感俏麗的服飾讓粉絲們一飽眼福！<br />\n<br />\n周子瑜昨天和團員們一起穿「制服」躍上東京巨蛋舞台，身著白色圖紋T-Shirt、搭配粉紅色百褶裙的她們，渾身散發青春洋溢的甜美氣息，而周子瑜雖然外罩一件黑色長版外套，全身包緊緊，但仍不忘和隊友合照曬盛世美顏狂撩粉！<br />\n<br />\n除了粉嫩制服裝超吸睛，周子瑜還換穿純白軍裝，藉由西裝上的墊肩設計烘托強大氣場，而短版上衣剪裁則讓她能隨著舞蹈動作、手一抬便露出22吋纖細螞蟻腰和緊實腹肌，整體造型酷帥有型又不失性感，十分迷人！<br />\n<br />\n或穿上義大利時尚品牌Gucci滿版Logo無袖短洋裝，混搭蕾絲透膚宮廷袖上衣，露出一雙穠纖合度的逆天美腿，配上過膝長靴，巧妙拉長腿部視覺線條，穿出宛如九頭身超模般的黃金比例，網友看了大讚：「戀愛了」、「這是什麼魔鬼身材」、「身材和臉蛋都無懈可擊！」"},{"pid":"5877d4611117e0965e54493ab6603382eb8db0c5","tid":1084472,"uid":59711,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T12:18:36.000Z","msg":"純文字討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa4ac0d80f8495bdeacf0dabcac21168511e99a","tid":1084472,"uid":94828,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T12:22:35.000Z","msg":"22吋飢民腰 逆天象腿"},{"pid":"738bebcaf6caa8a40a210ce5096f6b627ead418d","tid":1084472,"uid":74065,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T12:22:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>官方既野點會比你知真相<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rGng6ux.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrGng6ux.png&h=fb3c9eb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g8HH12T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg8HH12T.png&h=903762a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kqAZjPz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkqAZjPz.png&h=34748bab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n官方出既，連樣都重手P<br />\n呢緝相好多人拎黎吹奏神級美貌，P走埋佢最有特色既屎忽下爬同包包臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n望住fans吹奏緊P走晒個人特色既相好鬼搞笑<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YOsg6vi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYOsg6vi.png&h=3848ef8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n飯拍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yci4vW0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyci4vW0.png&h=9ac2a249&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無遮無掩飯拍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rY65ZQm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrY65ZQm.png&h=8fe574d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好睇少少飯拍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m9THhD9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm9THhD9.png&h=1bd26373&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講番隻腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由骨盆開始有少少出事 大腿單睇正常 <br />\n問題係腳型唔好睇 小腿太壯 同無腳眼<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CxkVCCf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCxkVCCf.png&h=b8d13439&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\ncut走小腿會好好多<br />\n所以通常佢既相都係大頭/半身<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mZtHhCh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmZtHhCh.png&h=4d37908a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋，睇同邊個比較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MRLKvXi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMRLKvXi.png&h=8acf70ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4vU7tJZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4vU7tJZ.png&h=5539e4c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拍埋呢兩件靚腳就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5WizTaF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5WizTaF.png&h=cecc8367&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有ching話近期瘦左，的確係幼左<br />\n箭嘴位係咪凹左，上面既小腿肌都平晒喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwAeTaQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwAeTaQ.png&h=596012c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9uEvrvR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9uEvrvR.png&h=52298bb4&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0eb6c1acdf5f3d666c08e13356716dfcc71e1d48","tid":1084472,"uid":15070,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"738bebcaf6caa8a40a210ce5096f6b627ead418d","tid":1084472,"uid":74065,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T12:22:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>官方既野點會比你知真相<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rGng6ux.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrGng6ux.png&h=fb3c9eb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g8HH12T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg8HH12T.png&h=903762a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kqAZjPz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkqAZjPz.png&h=34748bab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n官方出既，連樣都重手P<br />\n呢緝相好多人拎黎吹奏神級美貌，P走埋佢最有特色既屎忽下爬同包包臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n望住fans吹奏緊P走晒個人特色既相好鬼搞笑<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YOsg6vi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYOsg6vi.png&h=3848ef8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n飯拍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yci4vW0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyci4vW0.png&h=9ac2a249&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無遮無掩飯拍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rY65ZQm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrY65ZQm.png&h=8fe574d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好睇少少飯拍<br />\n<i